sections.title: What is Paid?
sections.content: IntroductionWhat is Paid?Copy page1. The BasicsBilling for AI: Unlike traditional billing methods, Paid is designed to bill based on the actual work performed by your AI systems.Flexibility: It supports many billing methods, such as one-time setup fees, recurring platform fees, per-user charges (seat-based), and usage-based charges.2. Key ComponentsAgentsThink of Agents as your AI “workers” (like a chatbot or an automated sales rep). They are the parts of your system that do the work.SignalsSign

sections.title: Usage
